item.description:
AUGUST PLAYDATE FOR ALL...
Let's get together and have some fun... we are going to have it at my house this time... in case of rain... please rsvp with a comment of snack or drink that you would like to bring... I will have a plastic swimming pool for any puggers that like to get wet.. like our Miss Molly...
I needed to sign up again for our subscription to Meet-up... I hate to ask; but it can get expensive.. I will have a donation can.. set out. If anyone wants to help contribute it would be greatly appreciated.
If you need to contact me my phone number is 641-3628. Pug hugs to all.. Patty

group.name: Manchester New Hampshire pug/small dog meet up group
